{"tid":1548364,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［緊急］全部人都話要831 cctv 但係有冇人諗過要依樣野","createTime":"2019-09-07T03:57:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T04:12:12.000Z","uid":277332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c8329fd1f1c66b575353812e36008f9f4718fbc0","tid":1548364,"uid":277332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T03:57:41.000Z","msg":"[/red]<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">就係依幾日墮樓案法現場既cctv</span>[/red]<br />\n甘多單可疑墮樓案 無論揾唔搵到現場/附近cctv都可能有幫助<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">]1.搵到</span>[/size=4<br />\n任何可疑人物(例如三四個拎著可疑手提袋既人士)/車輛/證據，當然唔洗講有甘大煲甘大<br />\n<br />\n[size=4]<span style=\"color: red;\">2.搵唔到</span></span><br />\n如果搵唔到亦只少可以排除一單，將注意力放係其他案件/新屋嶺到，唔洗比人spin走風向<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">3.案法現場/附近無cctv 或者影唔到自殺人士</span></span><br />\n可以間接證明有可疑<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有人拎走cctv/消失片段</span></span><br />\n同上，可以間接證明有可疑<br />\n<br />\n係依個cctv氾濫既時代要唔比cctv影到基本上冇可能，係案法現場返工既人，e.g. 7仔 銀行 餐廳 什到大廈保安，有能力check到cctv既人都希望可以睇睇，睇下有冇機會揾到任何線索"},{"pid":"b760c4408e3846f1fac8d2fbf779b9d6b9733a07","tid":1548364,"uid":277332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T03:58:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"00a25b474db977525051988667930de5cd9b7b81","tid":1548364,"uid":277332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T03:58:59.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"851059e4a536a0b203c71daae4fe8f2445492b56","tid":1548364,"uid":277332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T03:59:12.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"caf8617876d0f978c18e8a5a41a8bffd49b8c7de","tid":1548364,"uid":277332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T04:00:29.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"d375e3c9d420c259504d2243cccc8817b9674eaa","tid":1548364,"uid":277332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T04:01:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>[/red]<s